  "description": "An Asian-inspired noodle dish with a difference! You'll make deliciously succulent tofu balls by blending pan-fried mushrooms with tofu and garlic before roasting till golden in the oven. Serve on top of stir-fried vegetables and noodles with a drizzle of sticky soy-agave sauce. It's tofu time!",
